title: Ghost in the Shell seasons 1 and 2 ( Stand Alone Complex and 2nd
description:
This is seasons 1 and 2 of Ghost in the shell, ripped to high quality MP4s with H264 video and AAC audio. The spoken language is English, no 'Burned in' subtitles.
These are directly from the DVDs with a constant quality, not a constant size.

Note: The videos will not play in winamp, but will play with VLC and with media player classic found in the klite codec packs. 
They will play on ubuntu's video player without any problems.
They will play on the XBOX 360 if you download the media update (it will prompt you the first time you try to play a file).

3.90G for Stand alone Complex
3.57G for 2nd Gig

Enjoy, and be sure to check out the 3 movies for Ghost in the shell!
